From: Kamil Bienkiewicz <perceivalpercy@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 12:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] net: pcs: qcom-ipq9574: Accept qcom,ipq5332-pcs compatible

IPQ5332 uses the same UNIPHY PCS hardware block as IPQ9574 (PCS +
SerDes at the same register layout); the only difference is IPQ5332
exposes two instances (vs three on IPQ9574). Add the IPQ5332 compat
string to the match table so an IPQ5332 board DTS can use the same
driver without code changes.

Signed-off-by: Kamil Bienkiewicz <perceivalpercy@gmail.com>
---
--- a/drivers/net/pcs/pcs-qcom-ipq9574.c
+++ b/drivers/net/pcs/pcs-qcom-ipq9574.c
@@ -1050,6 +1050,7 @@
 static const struct of_device_id ipq9574_pcs_of_mtable[] = {
 	{ .compatible = "qcom,ipq9574-pcs" },
+	{ .compatible = "qcom,ipq5332-pcs" },
 	{ /* sentinel */ },
 };
 MODULE_DEVICE_TABLE(of, ipq9574_pcs_of_mtable);
